commit.message:
sparseset.c: Include config.h and system.h before sparseset.h.

2007-11-27  Bernhard Fischer  <aldot@gcc.gnu.org>

	* sparseset.c: Include config.h and system.h before sparseset.h.
	* sparseset.h: Remove inclusion of system.h.

From-SVN: r130622
